### List all persons (paginated, first page)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/persons
Accept: application/json

### List persons with search
GET http://localhost:5000/api/persons?search=Robert&page=1&pageSize=20
Accept: application/json

### Get person by ID
GET http://localhost:5000/api/persons/1
Accept: application/json

### Seed database from CSV
POST http://localhost:5000/api/persons/seed
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "csvFilePath": "/path/to/your/faces.csv"
}

### Recognize a face (replace path with actual image file)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/faces/recognize
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----FormBoundary

------FormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="image"; filename="test_face.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< /path/to/your/test_face.jpg
------FormBoundary--
